The paper discusses entity resolution in knowledge graphs, which involves database management (cs.DB), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), machine learning (cs.LG), information retrieval (cs.IR), and natural language processing (cs.CL). Therefore, these five sub-categories are the most likely to be associated with this paper.
